import PropTypes from "prop-types"; import s from "../Profile/Profile.module.css"; import defaultImg from "../../images/avatarka-pustaya-vk_23.jpg"; const Profile = ({ avatar = defaultImg, name, tag = "who knows", location, followers, views, likes, }) => (

{name}

{tag}

{location}

  • Followers {followers}
  • Views {views}
  • Likes {likes}
); Profile.propTypes = { defaultImg: PropTypes.string, name: PropTypes.string.isRequired, tag: PropTypes.string.isRequired, location: PropTypes.string.isRequired, followers: PropTypes.number.isRequired, }; export default Profile;
